views.createSql: CREATE VIEW `${VIEW_NAME}` AS SELECT body.*, latest_entry.* FROM body LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM body_entry AS entry WHERE entry.timestamp IN(SELECT MAX(E.timestamp) FROM body_entry AS E GROUP BY E.parent_id) GROUP BY entry.parent_id ORDER BY entry.entry_id DESC) AS latest_entry ON body.id = latest_entry.parent_id

CREATE VIEW `${VIEW_NAME}` AS SELECT routine.*, GROUP_CONCAT(exercise.name, ', ') AS exercise_names FROM exercise_with_routine ewr LEFT JOIN routine ON routine.id = ewr.routine_id LEFT JOIN exercise ON exercise.id = ewr.exercise_id GROUP BY routine.id
